Scriptune - Fortune on manna by an insane man.

A simple scripture fortune program with support for more than one book,
or even language.  Can be used with cgi to generate some happy or serious
quotes, depending on the date since Jan 1st 1970, and of course God.

Included is the  KJV New Testement.  Searching is also possible '-h' option
provides examples and instructions.

Install:
	'make' or make PREFIX=/path/to/wherever

followed by:
	'make install'

Author:
